## ✨ Features

✅ **Zero API Keys** - Uses free OpenStreetMap/Nominatim data
✅ **Local Store Search** - Find nearby stores within your specified distance
✅ **Online Retailers** - Compare prices from Amazon, iHerb, Vitacost, Thrive Market, and more
✅ **Natural Filter** - Only shows products with NO artificial ingredients
✅ **Cost Per Ounce** - All prices normalized for fair comparison
✅ **Shipping Included** - Online prices factor in delivery costs
✅ **CSV Export** - Download results for further analysis
✅ **Modern Web UI** - Beautiful, responsive Bootstrap interface
✅ **Mobile Friendly** - Works on all devices
✅ **CLI Support** - Command-line interface available
✅ **Real-time Search** - Get results instantly

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.8 or higher
- pip (Python package manager)
- Modern web browser

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository:**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/NBrown333/gummy-bear-price-finder.git
cd gummy-bear-price-finder
```

2. **Create a virtual environment:**
```bash
python -m venv venv

# On Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate

# On macOS/Linux:
source venv/bin/activate
